quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  26,67,"Dájúdájú àmì wà nínú ìyẹn. Síbẹ̀síbẹ̀ ọ̀pọ̀lọ́pọ̀ wọn kò jẹ́ onígbàgbọ́ òdodo."
  26,68,"Dájúdájú Olúwa rẹ, Òun mà ni Alágbára, Àṣàkẹ́-ọ̀run."
  26,69,"Ka ìròyìn (Ànábì) ’Ibrọ̄hīm fún wọn."
  27,40,"Ẹni tí ìmọ̀ kan láti inú tírà wà ní ọ̀dọ̀ rẹ̀ sọ pé: “Èmi yóò gbé e wá fún ọ ṣíwájú kí o tó ṣẹ́jú.” Nígbà tí ó rí i tí ó dé sí ọ̀dọ̀ rẹ̀, ó sọ pé: “Èyí wà nínú oore àjùlọ Olúwa mi láti fi dán mi wò bóyá mo máa dúpẹ́ tàbí mo máa ṣàì moore. Ẹnikẹ́ni tí ó bá dúpẹ́ (fún Allāhu), ó dúpẹ́ fún ẹ̀mí ara rẹ̀. Ẹnikẹ́ni tí ó bá sì ṣàìmoore, dájúdájú Olúwa mi ni Ọlọ́rọ̀, Alápọ̀n-ọ́nlé.”"
  27,41,"Ó sọ pé: “Ẹ pa á lójú dà fún un sí ìrísí mìíràn tí kò fi níí dá a mọ̀, kí á wò ó bóyá ó máa dá a mọ̀ tàbí ó máa wà nínú àwọn tí kò níí dá a mọ̀.”"
  27,42,"Nígbà tí (Bilƙīs) dé, wọ́n sọ fún un pé: “Ṣé bí ìtẹ́ rẹ ṣe rí nìyí?” Ó wí pé: "
  28,13,"A sì dá a padà sí ọ̀dọ̀ ìyá rẹ̀ nítorí kí ojú rẹ̀ lè tutù (fún ìdùnnú) àti nítorí kí ó má baà banújẹ́. Àti pé nítorí kí ó lè mọ̀ pé dájúdájú àdéhùn Allāhu, òdodo ni, ṣùgbọ́n ọ̀pọ̀lọ́pọ̀ wọn ni kò mọ̀."
  28,14,"Nígbà tí ó dàgbà dáadáa, tí ó di géńdé, A fún un ní ọgbọ́n àti ìmọ̀. Báyẹn ni A ṣe ń san àwọn olùṣe-rere ní ẹ̀san (rere)."
  28,15,"Ó wọ inú ìlú nígbà tí àwọn ará ìlú ti gbàgbé (nípa ọ̀rọ̀ rẹ̀).Ó rí àwọn ọkùnrin méjì kan tí wọ́n ń bara wọn jà. Èyí wá láti inú ìran rẹ̀. Èyí sì wá láti (inú ìran) ọ̀tá rẹ̀. Èyí tí ó wá láti inú ìran rẹ̀ wá ìrànlọ́wọ́ rẹ̀ lórí èyí tí ó wá láti (inú ìran) ọ̀tá rẹ̀. Mūsā kàn án ní ẹ̀ṣẹ́. Ó sì pa á. Ó sọ pé: “Èyí wà nínú iṣẹ́ Èṣù. Dájúdájú (èṣù) ni ọ̀tá aṣini-lọ́nà pọ́nńbélé.” {1}",1:[Ó ṣẹ̀ ní ààfin, ó sì yẹra nínú ilé fún Fir‘aon. Ó wá padà wọ inú ìlú lẹ́yìn ìgbà tí ọ̀rọ̀ náà ti kúregbé kúregbè.]
